Flag of Turkmenistan originally from the Open Clip Art website. Modified by User:Vzb83 using construction sheet at [1].

Colours:

  • green: PANTONE 16-6240 - Island Green TC - #28AE66
  • red: PANTONE 17-1654 - Poinsettia TC - #CA3745
  • yellow: PANTONE 14-0955 - Citrus TC - #FAAE29
  • black: PANTONE 19-4205 - Phantom TC - #383739
  • source: DECREE OF THE PRESIDENT OF TURKMENISTAN on February 14, 2000 № PP-3051. Regulations about the State flag of Turkmenistan, clause 3 (text - http://base.spinform.ru/show_doc.fwx?rgn=23643)
  • conversion to RGB on Pantone Colour Names - http://www.dspgroup.co.uk/material/ColourNamesPanton.htm
